---
title: Granny's Cheesy Beef Cottage Pie with Kumara-Broccoli Top
description: This is cottage comfort cuisine with a colourful twist, because why on Earth not? Not only does cheesy broccoli and kumara add gorgeous colour to this hardworking but rather ordinary looking dish, but it also adds a beautiful texture and amazing flavours as well.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b722c8c30006c42ca595453-ead47158.jpg
